items.title: Awesome Docker
items.content_text:
### Monitoring

*   [HertzBeat (⭐6.4k)](https://github.com/dromara/hertzbeat) - An open-source real-time monitoring system with custom-monitor and agentless.

### Wrappers / Other

*   [Preevy (⭐2.1k)](https://github.com/livecycle/preevy) - Preview environments for Docker and Docker Compose projects. Test your changes and get feedback from devs and non-devs (Product/Design) by deploying pull requests to the your cloud provider as part of your CI pipeline.

items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [xbira (⭐0)](https://github.com/ITAxReal/xbira) - Based on [bira (⭐180k)](https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/blob/master/themes/bira.zsh-theme), includes decorators for `git` status, user\@hostname, exit status of last command run and the current directory.

items.title: Awesome Neovim
items.content_text:
### (requires Neovim 0.5)

*   [aznhe21/actions-preview.nvim (⭐469)](https://github.com/aznhe21/actions-preview.nvim) - Fully customizable previewer for LSP code actions.

### Keybinding / Diagnostics

*   [echasnovski/mini.nvim#mini.clue (⭐7.5k)](https://github.com/echasnovski/mini.nvim/blob/main/readmes/mini-clue.md) - Module of `mini.nvim` to show next key clues. Has opt-in triggers, shows next key information after customizable delay, allows hydra-like submodes, and more.
